                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-01-11</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I stumbled upon this book while surfing on the web and I am so glad I did! I do not like cutsie, preachy books about how to live your life so I was a bit dubious about it at first. I had nothing to worry about. Reading this book is like sharing a cup of good coffee with a dear, and wise friend. It rolls all the wisdom you have heard through out your life, and then some, into one short, entertaining, enriching read. I will buy a copy for all the women in my life.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A warm hug!!!</div>
